# Product Specification Document
## ASYCUDA Write-Off Manifest Portal
**Version:** 1.0.0

---

## 1. Tech Stack

| Layer | Technology | Rationale |
|---|---|---|
| Frontend | React (Vite) | Fast build, component-based |
| Styling | Tailwind CSS | Utility-first, responsive |
| Icons | Lucide-React | Consistent, lightweight |
| State | React useState + Context | MVP-appropriate, no over-engineering |
| Backend | Python — FastAPI | Async-ready, OpenAPI auto-docs |
| Database | PostgreSQL via Supabase | Managed, real-time, auth built-in |
| Auth | Supabase Auth | Magic link + username/password |
| File Storage | Supabase Storage | Document uploads |
| Edge Functions | Supabase Edge Functions | Email notifications |
| External APIs | REST + API Keys via MCP endpoint registry | ASYCUDA, E-Valuator, E-Customs, Tradian |

