## 9. Security

| Concern | Implementation |
|---|---|
| API Key exposure | All external API calls via backend only. Keys in env vars. |
| Auth | Supabase JWT — all internal API routes require valid token |
| File uploads | Validated type (PDF/image), max 10MB, scanned via Supabase Storage |
| Input validation | Pydantic models on all FastAPI endpoints |
| Rate limiting | 10 requests/minute per user on /api/validate |
| Audit logging | Every state transition logged to audit_log table |
| CORS | Frontend domain whitelisted only |